title: Everyone's A Critic - Rob Tunbridge
description:
Rob Tunbridge is an unsigned singer/songwriter based in Chelmsford, 

Essex England.

You can find out more at: my space or search for Rob Tunbridge on you 

tube




This ZIP file contains the full album + Original Artwork in PDF Format


Tracks are MP3@192K and have been tested in i-tunes, windows media 

player, VLC Player

 5. Dangerous Games (to play) - Check out the video on you tube!
 6. I Saw Through The Moon
 7. Photographic
 8. Is It My Arms That You Miss?
 9. Everytime I think Of You
10. Where You Going To?
11. Sally & Jimmy
12. Running Tonight
13. I'm Not Listening
14. Invisible
